{"id":192049,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/示威老兵遭警方击中头部/","date":"2011-10-27T18:30:35Z","modified":"2011-10-27T18:30:35Z","title":"示威老兵遭警方击中头部","content":"<p>playfish 写道 &#8220;来自卫报、路透社等媒体的报导，美国加州奥克兰市（Oakland, California），警方向“占领奥克兰/Occupy Oakland”的示威人群投掷催泪瓦斯并用橡皮子弹开枪射击。曾两次在伊拉克服役的海军陆战队员、老兵Scott Olsen（24岁）被一枚催泪瓦斯弹击中头部，目前虽然伤势严重但情况稳定。据现场视频(YouTube)显示，一名警员更在Olsen受伤倒地、其他示威者纷纷上前准备救助时，向Olsen身边投掷了闪光弹。然而在当天晚上的新闻发布会上，警方表示并没有使用过闪光弹。&#8221;<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/199a89f6/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%81%E5%85%B5%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%87%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%B4%E9%83%A8&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F27%2F090226%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%81%E5%85%B5%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%87%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%B4%E9%83%A8&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F27%2F090226%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/117145837338/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/199a89f6/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/117145837338/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/199a89f6/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=xcuK8WdIFgs:hR1qNrApRM4:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=xcuK8WdIFgs:hR1qNrApRM4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><sm